---
/**
 * Static markup port of LandingPage.jsx CapturePhoneMockup (lines 58-122).
 * No interactivity in the React version either — pure visual.
 */
---

<div class="hiw-phone-frame">
  <div class="hiw-phone-island" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="hiw-phone-status" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="hiw-phone-time">9:41</span>
    <svg class="hiw-phone-signal" width="16" height="11" viewBox="0 0 19 12">
      <rect x="0"    y="7.5" width="3.2" height="4.5"  rx="0.7" fill="currentColor" />
      <rect x="4.8"  y="5"   width="3.2" height="7"    rx="0.7" fill="currentColor" />
      <rect x="9.6"  y="2.5" width="3.2" height="9.5"  rx="0.7" fill="currentColor" />
      <rect x="14.4" y="0"   width="3.2" height="12"   rx="0.7" fill="currentColor" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="hiw-phone-screen">
    <div class="hiw-phone-header">
      <div class="hiw-phone-eyebrow">Capture Mode</div>
      <div class="hiw-phone-heading">
        Record your highlights<br />and annotations
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-phone-viewfinder" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hiw-phone-page">
        <div class="hiw-phone-chapter">Chapter IV</div>
        We are what we repeatedly do.{' '}
        <span class="hiw-phone-highlight">
          Excellence, then, is not an act, but a habit.
        </span>{' '}
        And what is habit but the practiced imitation of virtue, day upon day, until the shape of one's soul has conformed itself...
      </div>
      <span class="hiw-bracket hiw-bracket-tl"></span>
      <span class="hiw-bracket hiw-bracket-tr"></span>
      <span class="hiw-bracket hiw-bracket-bl"></span>
      <span class="hiw-bracket hiw-bracket-br"></span>
      <div class="hiw-phone-detected">
        <span class="hiw-phone-detected-label">Passage detected</span>
        <div class="hiw-phone-glow"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="hiw-phone-hint">Mark up the passage first. Capture will ignore unmarked text.</p>

    <div class="hiw-phone-controls" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hiw-phone-manual">
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 20h9M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z" />
        </svg>
        <span>Manual</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hiw-phone-shutter"></div>
      <div class="hiw-phone-spacer"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hiw-phone-nav" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="hiw-phone-nav-icon">🏠</span>
    <span class="hiw-phone-nav-icon hiw-phone-nav-active">📷</span>
    <span class="hiw-phone-nav-icon">📋</span>
    <span class="hiw-phone-nav-icon">👤</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hiw-phone-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</div>
